Hello everyone,

As agreed during our Monday sync we would like to ask if its possible to have a check while having Stealthy DPI Enabled + making sure that analytic.emburse.com website is not added in Allowlist for DPI - with the latest test build that I've sent to Om on the other ticket.



Best regards,

Adrian Draghici |Technical Support Team Lead (EMEA/Asia/Aus)

Dear Harshvardhan,

Our intention was to see if any possible conflict is created between these apps that performs scans at the network level or act as VPN, proxies.
This suggestion was made in the interest of establishing which the next steps would be. Also, as suggested on the instacart.com ticket - is it possible to test with the client from 5941 since you already have this server version in place?


Best regards,
